  "texts": [
    "The acquisition system is the process through which an individual subconsciously acquires a second language.",
    "In this system, rules of the target language are formed and internalized unconsciously.",
    "The primary focus in this system is on the message conveyed, rather than on linguistic structure or grammar.",
    "Unlike the learning system, where there is assimilation and rationalization of rules of the second language as a result of formal teaching of grammar.",
    "Actually, there are many diverse models of second language acquisition."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}